# Audio-to-Text RAG for Podcast Search
This project processes podcasts, transcribes them, stores searchable embeddings, and allows topic-based search with timestamps.

## Features
- Audio-to-text conversion with Whisper
- Searchable text using Chroma DB
- Streamlit UI for user queries
- Timestamps for audio navigation

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
